      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically untouched, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road with its new best friend. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
