    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 B32 inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Power is delivered through a GKN-sourced M-Variable differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability the chassis is known for. Documented rod bearing service and a clean oil analysis confirm the internal health of this high-revving masterpiece. A showroom-quality example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
