      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts original, deep-gloss paint protected by a professional ceramic coating, completely free of swirls, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition, featuring supple, unscented leather, pristine carpets, and factory-clear displays with every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach; it includes a comprehensive service binder documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed exclusively by the master technicians at the dealership. With exceptionally low mileage and zero history of inclement weather exposure, this is a rare opportunity to own a preserved masterpiece. It drives as tightly and smoothly as the day it was delivered. Ready for the road or the show lawn.",
