      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood lies the S54B32 inline-six, a masterpiece featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS valve timing that pulls cleanly to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw shifts, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Maintained in concours condition, this chassis shows zero signs of thermal cycling fatigue or oxidation, making it a definitive collector-grade specimen for the driving purist.",
